    "description": "Jaypee Hospital Consulting Pvt Ltd, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Consultant Physician for our Jodhpur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Jaypee Hospital Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nJaypee Hospital Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Jaypee Hospital Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
